* If you aren't happy with the current name, you can rename your page using the "More Actions:" dropdown box, and selecting the "Rename Page" item.

Please follow the <nowiki>[[Artwork/Incoming/SubmissionGuidelines|Submission Guidelines]]</nowiki> before submitting your page.

If you wish, you can place the name of your concept, link and a single thumbnail to your project here. Otherwise, they will just be in the automatic subpage list above. Please, add your page at the bottom of the list.

Filling out the form with the desired page name and pressing the button will create said page using the template.
